# Project Structure Guidelines

## Directory Organization

The project follows Next.js 14+ App Router structure with shadcn/ui components and Framer Motion animations.

### Key Directories

- `src/app/`: Main application routes and pages using Next.js App Router
- `src/components/`: Reusable components
  - `ui/`: shadcn/ui components
  - `logos/`: Logo and brand-related components
- `src/lib/`: Utility functions and shared logic

### Component Organization

1. Place all shadcn/ui components in `src/components/ui/`
2. Custom components should be organized by feature in `src/components/`
3. Page-specific components go in same page directory in `/(components)` directory



### File References

Main configuration files:
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - shadcn/ui configuration
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
